Voice Assistant for Microsoft Identity Manager

The Voice Assistant for Microsoft Identity Manager is an Azure IoT Business Solution that uses Azure IoT, Azure Cognitive Services, Azure Serverless Services and other Azure Services along with Microsoft Identity Manager to empower IT Support staff with the ability to query Microsoft Identity Manager for common IT Service Desk, IT Admin requests.
